page.title: 12CHISLET HOMELIFE
page.content: Where I live is a nice quiet place except when tractors come by and it is good for playing games at my house. I have found some old coins and a solid gold ring it was worth 17 pounds. We are having a porch made on our back door but we have had a swimming pool built already. Our house is overfive hundred years old. A long time ago it was two cottages together we know that because it has got 14OO on one side and 1636 on the other. We are buying some land off the farmer and its got two ponds in it. On the other side we are buying a track which has got three barns and a piece of grass.
